{"word":"Antioch","slug":"antioch","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Antioch</b> 1. A city of Syria<br/> - Disciples first called Christians in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=11&verse=30'>Act 11:30</a> <br/> - Church in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=1'>Act 13:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=14&verse=27'>Act 14:27</a> <br/> - Barnabas and Paul make second visit to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=14&verse=28'>Act 14:28</a> <br/> - Dissension in church of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=35'>Act 15:35</a> <br/> - Paul and Peter's controversy at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=2&verse=15'>Gal 2:15</a> <br/> 2. A city of Pisidia. Persecutes Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=52'>Act 13:52</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=3&verse=11'>2Ti 3:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=14&verse=22'>Act 14:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=18&verse=22'>Act 18:22</a>"}]}